Text.string: Yeah, I know. Catch-A-Ride IS pretty awesome.
I do love stealin' stuff from bandits!
If you see him, tell Vaughn an old friend says, “Hey there, you sexy little toothpick.” He'll know who it's from.
I heard the COV hollering about some Great Vault. Sounds like a bunch of dumbass if ya ask me.
You're running with the Firehawk, huh? Pretty sweet gig. Lil's a local legend around Pandora. Saved our asses more times than I can count.
Always knew I'd get off that rock.
Don't you worry about Lil—she's tough as nails, with or without those tats.
We're gonna get those culty sumbitches, believe you me.
Glad we got this big ol' beast of a ship hummin'.
Mannnn, this ship is top-tier badass!

So, we're after the Vault again, huh? I don't know about them Eridians, but where I'm from, if you rig a skag trap, you might as well kill the poor bastard you catch, instead of leaving 'em for someone else to kill.
Whoo! Tyreen mighta got away, but you sure showed that Troy boy what-for!
Typhon De-freakin'-Leon! I can't believe he's still alive.
Nekrotafeyo huh? Never thought I'd see the day.
And here we thought Typhon DeLeon was lost forever.
Ava finally came into her own. Takes some longer than others, but she's got it now, boy! She's got it!
That Machine is quite a sight. Seems like them Eridians weren't screwing around.
Them Calypsos are Typhon DeLeon's kids. What the hell happened to 'em? They should've been the ones to save this damn galaxy, not tear it down.
An alien Machine. Man, I wish Scooter were alive to see this. He'd've loved to tinker with alien machinery.
Looks like it's time for the big'un. Go get 'er, VH.
Let's end this thing.
Well, come on then! We gotta save Pandora!
Ain't nothing left to say. Go get that God-bitch.
Typhon DeLeon, may that little hero rest in peace.
Lil's gone. Still don't seem real.
Well, Pandora's saved once again. Thanks to you, Vault Hunter.
Ava, she sure sprung up real fast, didn't she? Must've had a good role model—I'm looking at you, VH, you badass, you.
Still lots to do. Tons of COV to hunt down. And a ship to maintain! That'll keep us busy for a while.
Welp, it's been a wild ride, amigo.
Hey there, sugar boots.
Howdy, you.
Been wantin' to get my flirt on. You'll do fine.
Katagawa sure seems like a prick.
You think throwin' in with Rhys is the right call?
Looks like Atlas was doin' all right before Maliwan came in and botched things up real bad.
I don't know about that man Rhys. It's a sexy mustache, but my mama always says, “if he's got a 'stache, check for a rash.” Just sayin'.
What's Promethea like? If you find any sweet-ass rides, make sure you scan the parts at a Catch-A-Ride.
Good to see Maya's still kickin' ass and ain't botherin' to take names 'cause she's too busy kickin' ass.
I like this Ava kid. She's got spunk.
Mannnn, Athenas is pretty as hell!
I'm missin' some of my tools. If you see Ava, you tell her to stay the hell out of my garage!
So, you found one of them Vault Key fragments, huh? What's it taste like? Oh come on, you didn't sneak a lick? Come on!
Seems weird that a guy like Katagawa would throw his lot in with them cultists, but I'm sure he had his reasons.
Really wish I coulda seen the look on Katagawa's face when you blasted his pleasure yacht.
Katagawa in Zer0 cosplay? Ha-HA! Man, what a weirdo.
I wasn't totally on board with stepping into this corporate war, but it seems to be payin' off for us!
We're that much closer to the Vault now!
Maya... I can't... I can't even...
Ava's having a real hard time right now. But don't worry, I've got an eye on her.
We're gonna make those Calypsos pay for what they done!
So, it's onto Eden-6, huh? They say it's a paradise, but I'ma go ahead and call it “swamp ass central”.

I appreciate ya stoppin' by. Maya's death, well, it's been hard on all of us. But Ava, she's takin' it extra hard. Can't blame her. When my brother Scooter passed, I got in my car and just drove from light to dark, running over bandits and thinking of the good times.
Eden-6, huh? Looks like a whole planet of folks sufferin' from swamp-ass.
Hoo boy! Big ol' prison break, huh? Nice.
It's so good to see the B-Team in action. How's that big lunk Brick doin'? Is Mordecai still on the wagon? And Tina—still Tina, I'm a-guessing.
Ava's still wandering around the ship. I can hear her at night. Some things you just gotta work through on your own.
How's ol' Lil doing? With Maya gone and all? If I know her, she's buried the hurt deep inside, 'cause she knows that we're all countin' on her. That's why she's the Firehawk, powers or not.
What kinda fancy-pantses need a house that big?
Curse that Aurelia woman! Harpy's too nice a word for her. I got a few others that I'll whisper in yer ear sometime.
That Troy Calypso—if I run into him, he's gonna be two balls short of a... I'm a cut his boys, that's what I'm trying to say.
I like this Clay guy. He knows what's up.
Them Jakobs boys sure are ready for a fight.
Who doesn't love a good resistance? Not that ya need a reason to kill bandits.
Way to back up them Jakobs loyalists down there.
Wonder why Jakobs decided to set up on Eden-6 anyway.
Shootin' her own brother? That Aurelia lady was bad news, amigo.
Guess it's back to Pandora to save our science lady, huh?
Poor Tannis. I think she's tougher than she lets on, though. She'll be all right.
I feel like things are coming to a close. Strap in, amigo. It's about to get bumpy. I can feel it in my bones.
I'm not tryin' to say that Tannis being kidnapped was a bright side, per se, but it did seem to snap Ava outta her funk. I seen her practicing in Marcus's armory every free moment she's got.
Whoo! That looked like one HELL of a ride, VH!
Glad to see my sculpted little Vaughn ain't lost his edge.
You sure tore up that bandit party right good, VH.
All else aside, that Carnivora thing is sweet as hell!
Tannis is a Siren?! What the hell?! You think you know a gal.
Those Calypsos, there ain't nothin' they care about—that's what makes 'em so damn dangerous.
You found the map, huh? Well all right, nice going!
Lil... her powers are gone. The rakk's really hit the turbine, ain't it?
That Clay guy's got style out the wazoo! And you know what I'd like to do to his wazoo. Heh, yeah.
My ship's sounding mighty fine with that new AI you installed.
You don't need a fancy pistol to see what I got goin' on.
The hell you standin' around for?! Go find Tannis!
If I had a sixer and a Carnivora all to myself, I'd take the road trip from hell.
End of the road, VH. Hope you're ready, hon.
That twiggy li'l Troy boy's dead, huh? We didn't get Tyreen, but hey, better one than none.
“Nekro-ta-fay-o”? What kinda dumbass name for a planet is that?
Typhon fathered them hellions? Shit. That's some heavy stuff, amigo.
Pandora needs you, Vault Hunter. That's all there is to it. Go kick some God-Queen ass.
Thanks for helpin' fix up Sanctuary!
Bravo, VH. You saved the goddamn galaxy, how's it feel?
[humming] That's the song he taught me.
Scooter! Can you hear me, you little bastard?! I miss you!
Hoo! THAT was a good night, heh-heh!
I miss you.
So we got ourselves a new ally? Is he a looker?
Maya? I ain't seen that sparkfire in a time!
A laser mounted to a big-ass asteroid? Damn!
You sure saved Rhys's—I assume—fine ass.
Maya... damn. Nothin' to say.
You freed Sir Hammerlock, did ya? I can't understand half the words that bastard says, but he sounds smart, don't he?
What's a mansion look like, anyway?
Got a job for ya, hon. Come on over.
Need some work? I got something for ya.
You busy, Vault Hunter? If not, swing on by!
Howdy!
Oh hey, y'all.
What's up, VH?
How's it hangin'?
You good?
Sick weapon you got there, VH.
Now THAT is a damn fine weapon.
Got somethin' for ya.
Could you do me a favor?
Cookin' up a little mission for ya.
Fancy a little shootin' and lootin'?
Hey, VH. Got a job that needs doin'.
How's that thing goin, VH?
Gettin' that job done?
Quit standin' around and get the job done, hon.
You let me know when you're done with that thing.
Don't you have somethin' to do, hon?
I love to watch you go.
Later, Vault Hunter.
Bye-bye, now.
Squish squish, jellyfish.
In a while, crocodile.
So long.
Y'all come on back now.
Bye.
Toodles.
Talk at ya later.
This here's the Catch-A-Ride! We got wenches with wrenches, and cars for days!
Welcome to the Catch-A-Ride! You'd look better in a rig!
I know you got a need, get you some speed!
Catch a ride, amigo!
Get yer feet outta the dirt and onto some pedals!
Fully loaded and ready to roll! Catch you a ride!
Get some wheels and roll out!
We got sexy metal steeds for your needs!
Catch-A-Ride's got the finest shafts and cranks! Heh heh.
You'd look even better with some wheels.
Walkin's for chumps!
Ya don't need no license for these babies, go hog wild!
I'll give you a whole seat, but all you're gonna need is the edge!
Catch a ride before you catch yer death!
You'd look a lot sexier in a hunka chunka steel and wheels!
Bullets and barrels, flamethrowers and shields, we got what'cha need!
Kick the tires and kick some ass!
Let's make some roadkill, amigo!
We got the war machines of your dreams at the Catch-A-Ride!
Our rides are the tits, amigo! Get you one and show 'em what-for!
You'll get there faster with a set of wheels!
Get where you're goin' in style with Catch-A-Ride!
You got the feels for some new wheels?
Getcher rear in gear and Catch-A-Ride, you beautiful sumbitch.
Nothin' but the beefiest, baddest rides around for you, amigo!
Lemme whip you up somethin' badass.
Put some steel under your heel at the Catch-A-Ride!
I got you covered at the Catch-A-Ride. You can't beat “free”!
We got the goods under the hood. Come Catch-A-Ride!
Anytime you need a ride, come see me. I'll get yer motor runnin'.
Quitcher stumblin' and get ta rumblin'—Catch-A-Ride!
Momma always said nothin' good ever happens after 10,000 RPM, but what momma don't know won't hurt her!
Armor? Check. Guns? Check. Speed? You bet yer ass! Catch-A-Ride!
Sure they ain't got cupholders, but my runners'll haul ass like a house on fire!
Kickin' dust is fer chumps—you need wheels, amigo!
Let loose with the boost! Catch-A-Ride!
Wheels, seats, guns—unless yer lookin' fer trunk space, these babies got it all!
When thrust is a must, you come see ME.
Catch-A-Ride! 'Cause NO ONE likes cardio.
My cars're digistructed from one hunnert percent recycled steel, rubber, and you don't wanna know what else.
If you don't wanna get eaten, Catch-A-Ride! 'Cause nothin' eats cars 'cept fer Earl, and he don't get out much.
Walkin' 'round Pandora's how you get yerself killed. Get inna rollcage and kick some ass!
Nothin' attracts the members of whatever-sex-ya-like like a few tons of roarin' steel on wheels. Catch-A-Ride! Heh. Get it?
We got runners for gunners—get you one!
Catch you a sick-ass ride right over here!
Don't use your dumb old legs. Get you some wheels!
